11 (ii) Members appointed by the governor, as
12 follows:
13
14 (A) Two (2) members representing Wyoming
15 county governments;
16
17 (B) Two (2) members representing Wyoming
18 cities and towns;
19
20 (C) One (1) member representing Wyoming
21 special districts;
22
